data.description: All brick 4 bedroom 2 bathroom open concept home in a nice quiet 2 cul de sac neighborhood zoned for top rated schools. It is located just 25 minutes from Hurlburt field and 50 minutes from Pensacola NAS and Eglin AFB. An elegant kitchen is complete with granite counter tops, plenty of storage space, and all stainless steel appliances including the refrigerator. The spacious master bedroom features an on-suite master bathroom with separate shower and tub, his and her walk-in closets, his and her sink, and a linen closet. There are 3 spacious rooms on the opposite side of the house. The second bathroom has a tub/shower combo, linen closet, and a coat closet adjacent to the bathroom. The living room and dining room have laminate wood flooring while the kitchen and laundry room are both tiled
